{
  "texts": [
    "The outputs are the mean and variance of obstacle clearance distribution.",
    "We collected 80k point-cloud instances.",
    "In each of them, we used N p = 50 control sequences with randomized robot initial state to generate trajectories along which we computed the ground-truth worst-case obstacle clearance.",
    "This yielded a total of ≈ 6M training points(point-cloud times N p times random initial states).",
    "The total training time was ≈2.5 h, following the procedure in Secs."
  ]
}